{"tid":1358373,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［721開槍證據］克警無預警下天橋開槍","createTime":"2019-07-24T02:08:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T13:20:09.000Z","uid":3513,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6a26e494c9d555e17306abd672f085ec42f43064","tid":1358373,"uid":3513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:08:40.000Z","msg":"警方驅散干諾道西示威者<br />\n天橋上無預警下向人群開槍<br />\n<br />\n《Now 新聞》昨晚播出警方在7月21日上環驅散示威者時，有橋上警員在未有示警下開槍。獨媒記者當晚亦在現場拍得相關片段，清楚見到有持槍的速龍小隊在中區警署外的天橋上，在無預警下向地面的示威者開槍。<br />\n<br />\n片段：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2JKbntY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2JKbntY&d=gHNHb7VIn83nczLIzOZu1RSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=6ece4f41\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2JKbntY</a><br />\n<br />\nSource : 獨媒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9aeOGD9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9aeOGD9.png&h=6e1df45c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f3a55270b63d6f79b2f2107560c63ce3f93d96e3","tid":1358373,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:12:04.000Z","msg":"元朗手足有野講 727去唔去都入黎睇下<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1357311\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1357311</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b4c9fd947360a1001a681e016ebad60855383c26","tid":1358373,"uid":165246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:12:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請大家一定要記得！！！！<br />\n１。全面撤回逃犯條例<br />\n２。撤銷暴動定性<br />\n３。釋放被捕義士並承諾永不追究<br />\n４。全面實行雙普選<br />\n５。成立獨立調查委員會追究黑警責任＋徹查警黑勾結元朗站暴打站內市民<br />\n6 。721上環對示威者開36槍 義士被狗開槍擊中<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif